    <stitle>No Idle APU/HVAC System - Troubleshooting - Chassis</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="troubleshoot" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Chassis</title>
        <para>
            <emph type="bold">Vibration</emph>
        </para>
        <seqlist style="alphalc">
            <item>
                <para>Loose / damaged vibration mount - Remove and replace.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Loose engine foot bolts - Remove thread locking compound, re-install and torque.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Loose / damaged drive pulley - Remove and replace pulley (install new key).</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Loose / damaged generator - Replace generator.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Incorrect exhaust tail pipe position - Re-position to center of extraction point.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Internal engine damage - Engine Service Manual S12020.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Uneven generator mounting feet - Loosen generator bearing housing and re-align mounting feet.
                </para>
            </item>
        </seqlist>
        <para>
            <emph type="bold">Rattling, noise</emph>
        </para>
        <seqlist style="alphalc">
            <item>
                <para>Loose body panel / missing bolts - Replace / tighten.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Loose engine bolts / damaged part(s) - see Engine Service Manual S12020.</para>
            </item>
            <item>
                <para>Loose / damaged generator - Inspect for damage replace and tighten.</para>
            </item>
        </seqlist>
    </svcproc>
